{"tid":1294053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"將香港變為中國禁地","createTime":"2019-07-07T17:31:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T17:42:35.000Z","uid":274412,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e30f4bdb2d322925c988c1a0a46c437672cb3d4e","tid":1294053,"uid":274412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:31:36.000Z","msg":"其實每日150個中國大陸人嚟港，我地應該當佢係脫北者，<br />\n見到中國客要友善對待，將佢地唔知嘅同佢地分享<br />\n遊行應該唱中國國歌，特別對住班遊客，一係吸引佢地注意，二係將佢唱到變主題曲<br />\n仲有咩方法<br />\n要令中國好驚有人嚟香港"},{"pid":"49f91efd6418c189ea60d2a4a7ca253d00f42944","tid":1294053,"uid":6195,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:41:14.000Z","msg":"脫北<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲150蝗9成落嚟拎著數，<br />\n<br />\n對香港既嘢不聞不問，<br />\n<br />\n一有時間就返大陸飲飲食食。<br />\n<br />\n示威抗爭，哈，佢當你班港燦傻西咋，<br />\n<br />\n每個月袋袋平安啦，踩你都有味啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17ea706833020ff5b08d667b7dbfd74aabf8eec0","tid":1294053,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:42:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}